body.p: scaling factor for hepatic function. 1.0: normal hepatic function; <1.0: reduced hepatic function
Scaling factor to vary UGT2B4 activity. 1.0: unchanged activity; < 1.0 decreased activity; >1.0 increased activity.
Scaling factor to vary UGT1A9 activity. 1.0: unchanged activity; < 1.0 decreased activity; >1.0 increased activity.
Scaling factor to vary CYP3A4 activity. 1.0: unchanged activity; < 1.0 decreased activity; >1.0 increased activity.
